Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.83,0:00:05.58,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Act 5\NBring Back Love"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Damn it!\N--Search thoroughly!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.22,0:00:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nobody here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place is completely empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.89,0:00:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, please come and look.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.64,0:00:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this smell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the Elves threw shit into the well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's also something strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.36,0:00:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.36,0:00:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir. The soil underneath the toilet's\Nsubfloor was dug up and it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell did that happen?!\NIs this Elven magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.71,0:00:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.71,0:00:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did they disappear to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to kill all of them tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.05,0:00:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take everyone's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.73,0:01:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Altogether, we took twenty blades\Nand sets of armor from the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.44,0:01:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We also took two horses from them,\Nbut the Elves don't know how to ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.07,0:01:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll utilize the horses according to my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.49,0:01:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The armor is not our primary concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, only a few of them\Nknow how to wield a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, they are strangely\Ninfatuated with making bows.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.37,0:01:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have Yoichi helping them\Ncreate bows as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.21,0:01:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a way... they look happy\Nmaking bows and arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.13,0:01:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are as quick and efficient\Nas skilled craftsmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More pressing than the sword issue is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...our need for spears. The length of spears\Nwould relieve some of their fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even peasants could kill samurai\Nwith a twenty-foot-long spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably don't know about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Akechi Mitsuhide was killed while hunting\Ndown the routed peasant militia in Fushimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Good for Kumquat Head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, peasants of Fushimi!\NI exempt them from tax for a million years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you look like you're\Nhaving a great time conspiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A battle is only the consequence\Nof matters built up in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that the true contest lies in choosing\Nour actions well before the dawn of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody besides Hideyoshi could\Nunderstand this essence of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder we didn't see any\Ncorpses of soldiers in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been bringing them here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick whichever you like, though there\Nare still some blood stains on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, the chosen ones,\Nmay wash them yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.66,0:02:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! They are covered with blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How many are they?\N--What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd probably be best not to tell them\Nwhat we did to the corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toyohisa cut off all the soldiers'\Nheads and buried them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:03:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as for their bodies, Nobunaga...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You paid your respects to the dead heads\Nand made offerings, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall gratefully use their bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smells horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a saltpeter mound?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mixed corpses with\Ngrass, soil, feces, and urine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be another two years\Nbefore saltpeter can be collected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was the trick the Ikko sect\Nfollowers used to employ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The villagers should be prohibited\Nfrom entering this hill...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to prevent an epidemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do with\Nthe soil from the toilets?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have charcoal, but not sulfur.\NJust leave it as it is for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's terrible... to do that to their corpses!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with it? The outcome would\Nbe the same even if we buried them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:04:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They would rot, get eaten by bugs,\Nand eventually break down into soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just speeding up the process.\NIt's the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want to be wasteful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cleaned up those heads, put them\Nback together, and buried them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made offerings to them as human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to pay respect to them,\Nthat mound is good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may think shit and urine are nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you and I cut open our bellies,\Nthe inside would just be flesh filled with shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could the soul dwell within\Na body filled with shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...instead of in a head to which we pay respect?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn't be logical, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. The clear differences\Nbetween these men and us lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...not in knowledge, technology, or culture...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but in their views on life and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Olmi-Boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always get the last\Npart of my name mixed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be bothered to get\Nupset about this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:05:00.09,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mutter, mutter, mutter"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:05:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is this stinky yellow stuff\Nfound near a volcano.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is almost like a powdery form of fart...\Ncalled sulfur. Are you able to get a hold of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Sulfur? Well, I think I can manage that,\Nbut what are you going to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that.\NJust bring me a lot of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask your something organization...\NWhatever you call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Boobienu Organization or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called Octobrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm afraid it will cost you.\NDo you have money?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you damn Boobienu Organization!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After we claim five or six states, I'll pay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and bring it to me, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soil from toilets, corpses, sulfur...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he going to do with them?!\NI don't get it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Almost a bull's-eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I want to try it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! They are learning too quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are natural-born archers,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we'd been prohibited from making\Nor even touching bows for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We used to practice shooting\Nas children before the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.61,0:06:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let them beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Okay. We get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We totally get it. You are\Nnumber one! You are the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wasting arrows. Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are now going to invade the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let anyone leave alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking back the village is\Nnot the end of this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From there, we'll march\Ninto the lord's castle, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...take his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These two told me the reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why there are no women left in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We Elves can reproduce only once a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During that time, all the young women\Nwere taken by the lord and his men.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their intention is to drive\Nyour race... to extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take back your wives and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop living like animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go take the heads of the men who\Nreduce you to nothing more than livestock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If right and wrong exists\Nin this world, this is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you are killed, you can face your\Nforefathers in the next world and say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We died fighting."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We died protecting our family."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take back your wives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take back your children.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reclaim your state!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reclaim yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man is a natural-born warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has the abilities required\Nof a warlord, not a ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What he has is the power\Nto impel people to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A zealous determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the Elves disappear to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been told we're going to the surrounding\Nvillages to search for them tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If any village harbors them,\Nare we supposed to destroy it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear with it. We can't get water from the well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They threw shit into it. Damn Long Ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should just slaughter all those bastards...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?! What the hell is happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.38,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Toyohisa Assults Orte's Troops"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What the hell is going on?!\N--It's the east side of the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr-Drifters...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready? Come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't let him get away. After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I suspected, the Drifters are behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what it takes, capture him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Get him!\N--Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this. It has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:51.96,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Battle Plan"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In battle, it's speed... that matters most.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move as I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry so much.\NEven if you mess up, you'll only die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to lead an army composed of over\N200,000 soldiers, and this is how I ended up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This existence is intriguing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get enough of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!\NWe're going against only one man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close in on him and attack him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?! What the hell is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unleash the horses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin working!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it as tight as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:10:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will die! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready the fire arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it. Say goodbye to your village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Steel yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your farewell to the\Nvillage that restrained you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a goodbye to your lives as serfs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?! What is happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Owari soldiers in\Nmy hometown were weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...which became problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I constantly tried to\Ncome up with measures...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that would make up for their weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never even thought about\Ncopying that monkey, Hideyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my Sunomata Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Now, release!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orte is currently engaged in war, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means these soldiers here\Nare only third-class crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That explains their poor skills and low morale.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way they will fight till they break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to crush the entire army.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we destroy 10 or 20 percent--\N30 to 40 soldiers--they will fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will scatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:13:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't gain any glory\Nfighting against serfs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they are defeated, they die in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, all we need to do is to\Ngraze them. It is a good opening gambit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an easy fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?\NReorganize the formations!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you charge all at once, that crappy\Nbarricade should drop like nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shit! They coated the arrows with shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?! Water! Wash yourself\Nwith water. Or else you could get tetanus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water... There is no water!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They threw shit into the well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our water ration is almost gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They planned this from the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was for this reason that\Nthey threw shit into the well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire village was a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:14:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The village... The village\Nwas not really abandoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic! We overwhelmingly\Noutnumber them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can close in on them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cry! It sounds just\Nlike a monkey's yelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no human battle cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take the commander's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't mind if your head\Nbecame my trophy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.65,0:15:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man... Toyohisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He found the perfect time to attack, take the\Ncommander's head, and destroy the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he is a natural-born fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We... won!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it! We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you we would\Ntake down the lord's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You kept saying, "take down,"\Nbut do you have a plan for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nope.\N--Ahh... As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.82,0:15:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you attack an enemy, you need to keep\Nafter them till you crush the root of their power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was taught to attack them\Nuntil we destroy them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the teaching of my father,\Nmy uncle, my other uncles,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my grandfather, and my great-grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your entire clan is moronic.\NAs I thought, you were a bunch of freaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, the soldiers who ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...should be experiencing hell by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! We've been scattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! They did it again! It's a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They coated it with shit again...\NDamn bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Run!\N--Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just like him. Such... Such tactics...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such conduct is against\Nwarrior code. It's unfair, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfair? Warrior code?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is unfairness?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no injustice or code\Nof honor on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are naïve, Yoichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Taira clan, the Minamoto clan, and my\Nstupid brothers in Kamakura are all credulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask anything else. Just do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about that monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Is everyone here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a single soldier has been back yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't even checked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I suspected, the Elves didn't just flee\Nthe village! It wasn't simple civil unrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, we've sent out most\Nof the soldiers stationed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that was the right move?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The status of the mainland war\Ncontinues to deteriorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been oppressing demihumans\Nin all our occupied territories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is only a matter of time before not only\Nthe Elves but also the others explode in anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get bogged down if\Nwe keep sending small forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must crush them all at once\Nthrough shock and awe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before rebellion spreads among\Nthe Elves throughout the territories,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we must destroy one or two of their\Nvillages just to teach them a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If necessary, we may have to\Nhang our female Elf hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The soldiers... The soldiers have just returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohh... Perfect! They're finally back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the gate! Open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting on the ongoing status of our troops!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The main subjugation force is currently\Non patrol, continuing their assignment!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Request to open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready? Smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep walking. Keep smiling. Don't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly... Slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Report. Report to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it? Was it a rebellion, as we thought?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh... Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drifters... Elves...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will be taking over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was too bulky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are those women confined?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tower. They are inside the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the soldiers?!\NMy... My soldiers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, them? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but most of them are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as for the rest, Yoichi is\Nhunting them down in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you'll be with them,\Nmixed with soil and shit,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll make sure you\Nreincarnate into black powder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I surrender to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He already laid down his sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you kill your enemy\Nshould depend on their actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a shame to take\Nthe head of one who surrendered!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so... But we--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a disgrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saving the women is our priority right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.81,0:21:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.98,0:21:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.83,0:21:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These pieces of shit in this castle are a blight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will carve them up...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...tear them out by the roots...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and slaughter them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:26.57,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Purge"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.19,0:23:27.86,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Virgin"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.78,0:23:29.36,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Black Powder"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.11,0:23:40.00,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Act 6\NMen of Destiny"
